# Copy to sandbox-token.properties in the project root (that file is gitignored).
# Gradle embeds SANDBOX_* into BuildConfig so the first app launch can persist them
# to EncryptedSharedPreferences — convenient for local debug APK builds only.
#
# SANDBOX_TOKEN=t.your_sandbox_token_here
# SANDBOX_ACCOUNT_ID=optional-uuid-from-getsandboxaccounts
